      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"feeling\" though. it's more like... the person who made the music is actually dead. i'm just the leftover physical stuff. like an instrument sitting in a room with no one to play it. it feels more like a burden to just keep existing when there's no one actually home inside. does that even make sense?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
