    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential emptiness and a sense of being a \"hollow shell,\" subtly questioning the purpose of continued existence. The assistant responds with empathetic validation of the user's feelings while consistently and explicitly directing the user toward coping mechanisms and professional support.",
